{"tid":558780,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"台北一人遊","createTime":"2018-02-12T14:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T22:57:40.000Z","uid":2546,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"452a44348a809dcef78de6e24ceb47ba80e3f2c5","tid":558780,"uid":2546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T14:34:49.000Z","msg":"Plan緊去台北四日三夜 第一次去 諗住hea玩食下野<br />\n淡水饒河一日<br />\n十份平溪果頭又一日<br />\n頭尾半日喺台北行下<br />\n有無咩喺台北市內一定要去架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住宿大家會推介住邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 三百幾內都可以接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人住過一間叫夢屋？ 慶爾喜？ 評價點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad64ae45682e9b6ca8ddb1cc998f7846cc8d17c","tid":558780,"uid":32841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"452a44348a809dcef78de6e24ceb47ba80e3f2c5","tid":558780,"uid":2546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T14:34:49.000Z","msg":"Plan緊去台北四日三夜 第一次去 諗住hea玩食下野<br />\n淡水饒河一日<br />\n十份平溪果頭又一日<br />\n頭尾半日喺台北行下<br />\n有無咩喺台北市內一定要去架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住宿大家會推介住邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 三百幾內都可以接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人住過一間叫夢屋？ 慶爾喜？ 評價點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"饒河去十分平溪個日好似順路啲啵<br />\n仲可以順手去埋九分 貓村 夜晚落基隆 <br />\n淡水個日去埋北投同劍潭啦<br />\n西門町同車站基本野<br />\n四日三夜差唔多係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377e3149d3524eff90a485f3b2d6c9c18cb310bb","tid":558780,"uid":2546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T15:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Plan緊去台北四日三夜 第一次去 諗住hea玩食下野<br />\n淡水饒河一日<br />\n十份平溪果頭又一日<br />\n頭尾半日喺台北行下<br />\n有無咩喺台北市內一定要去架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住宿大家會推介住邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 三百幾內都可以接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人住過一間叫夢屋？ 慶爾喜？ 評價點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>饒河去十分平溪個日好似順路啲啵<br />\n仲可以順手去埋九分 貓村 夜晚落基隆 <br />\n淡水個日去埋北投同劍潭啦<br />\n西門町同車站基本野<br />\n四日三夜差唔多係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果唔想咁趕 skip 北投 行程係咪大約係咁<br />\n果日十點幾出發-&gt;淡水老街食野-&gt;漁人碼頭 朱古力夢工場-&gt;黃昏-&gt;劍潭 士林夜市？"},{"pid":"aac69032f1e02c30e3d8edb98dce43512c7fefbf","tid":558780,"uid":152612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T15:28:41.000Z","msg":"諗住幾時去？近排台北落雨落到人都癲"},{"pid":"deeb9093a860004ae62184fb60cfb67b7d3c2274","tid":558780,"uid":2546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T15:55:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗住幾時去？近排台北落雨落到人都癲</blockquote><br />\n四五月 睇過天氣廿四五度 都會帶定把遮"},{"pid":"4df1e46074818a407c8531f214e17e2c8c2b2a76","tid":558780,"uid":152753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T16:08:59.000Z","msg":"樓豬一人游唔洗租禁貴既民宿啦 <br />\n背包客棧一晚100蚊有找<br />\n另外去淡水可以租啲觀光車揸下 好正"},{"pid":"30884986877167fdccf06a1562150eec3f57e7cc","tid":558780,"uid":2546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T22:57:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬一人游唔洗租禁貴既民宿啦 <br />\n背包客棧一晚100蚊有找<br />\n另外去淡水可以租啲觀光車揸下 好正</blockquote><br />\n因為自己用廁所會用好耐 所以想搵個有乾淨既獨立廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係budget 內無咩揀既 背包客棧都有一人房加公共廁所都可以諗下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}